, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/97907/', '', 'Ticagrelor, Betrixaban, Clopidogrel, Cilostazol, Iloprost, Lepirudin, Acenocoumarol, Urokinase, Cangrelor, Dipyridamole, Caplacizumab, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, More', 1767369485);
